data.value: Sometimes some patients can be needs special attention cause of different illness. For example Covid-19, if patient has covid virus, he/she need to be far away from other peoples to protect who has not any covid virus persons. In this situation doctors or any health employee can want stay away from patient who has covid. This project offers to remote patient care oppurtunity for that kind of situations.
